{"tid":1424458,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家一人一信給在 RTHK 的利君雅女士","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T10:49:29.000Z","uid":209337,"like":112,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6f079521c4693e3a785f0f6d326696d1c385cc4f","tid":1424458,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:55:12.000Z","msg":"早幾日，rthk 同事都講緊，其實日日都會收到好多人對利君雅嘅投訴信，好多人寫信佢講佢亂問問題，唔講都知係咩人有心寫，想做死佢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實我每一次睇直播，都好驚見唔到利君雅</span></span>，好驚佢被消失，好驚無人問問題，我都相信好多記者行家都好勁，一定會迫到講大話的人講真話，但係利君雅真係走得好前，句句到肉！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真理，係要用勇氣去爭取！</span></span><br />\n所以見到薯伯伯個post ，都覺得好感動有人真係有行動，去支持佢！<br />\n大家，記住，有勇氣的人有良心的人，才是香港一直的核心價值！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U9YaveE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU9YaveE.png&h=b7312a29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽聞最近很多人向香港電台的敢言記者，利君雅女士，作出無理的指控及投訴。<br />\n大家花少少時間，隨便寫一句話給香港電台，支持一下利君雅女士。<br />\n港台電郵：ccu@rthk.hk"},{"pid":"4e34a2cd10d66cef1b7e1eb42b0d9beada211e1b","tid":1424458,"uid":234719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198156923b3061df0b124ccfe22555d1d6411517","tid":1424458,"uid":294523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:56:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d6b74f9339405d98358e249516765e32bc70be4","tid":1424458,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:56:29.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"a49deb35cad8b05a0262c6aef565de28bb5e000f","tid":1424458,"uid":281230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:56:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"af44ab3f82b79700ce4ac130ada506cd7916500b","tid":1424458,"uid":270830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:56:41.00